                    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
                        <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
                            <figure class="fiu-quote fiu-quote--employer">
                                <blockquote class="fiu-quote__blockquote">
                                    "Have a plan of what it is that you would like for your student to learn while they are with you, speak to them about what their goals are. Be ready to offer extra time and support to make sure that you get the best out of them."
                                </blockquote>
                                <figcaption class="fiu-quote__caption">
                                    Employer
                                    <span class="fiu-quote__caption-description">Organisation</span>
                                </figcaption>
                            </figure>
                        </div>
                        <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
                            <img src="https://das-roi-tool-prototype.herokuapp.com/public/images/image1.jpg" class="fiu-panel__image" alt="" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
​
                    <a href="#" class="fiu-button fiu-button--employers fiu-button--outlined govuk-!-margin-top-4 govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">See more stories from businesses like yours </a>
​
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>